---
import binUnit1 from '../../assets/images/BinUnits/binUnit1.png';
import Image from 'astro/components/Image.astro';
import bin from '../../assets/images/BinUnits/GallerySlider/Big/TlvP317P268B.png';
import AcordeonItem from '../unitComponents/AcordeonItem';
import img1 from "../../assets/images/BinUnits/ProvBU2.jpg";
import img2 from "../../assets/images/BinUnits/ProvBU3.jpeg";
import img3 from "../../assets/images/BinUnits/ProvBU4.jpg";
---
<div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center mt-10">
    <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 overflow-visible px-8 lg:px-20 xl:px-52 items-center">
        <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-10">
            <div>
                <img src={img1.src} alt="" class="rounded-lg">
            </div>
            <div class="w-full flex flex-col justify-center">
                <h1 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold">Integrated Control Over Aggregate Flow </h1>
                <br>
                <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-extralight text-grisT text-justify" >Triaso® bin feeders are fully managed by the central
                     control system, allowing real-time adjustment of
                      material output for each bin. Through synchronized
                       coordination, the system ensures exact proportions
                        are delivered to the mixing process according to
                         the selected recipe. Operators can monitor and
                          adjust each bin’s behavior from the control
                           cabinet, enabling instant response to production
                            needs or material changes. This seamless integration reduces waste,
                             ensures mix consistency, and streamlines the entire asphalt production
                              cycle.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <img src={img3.src} alt="" class="rounded-lg">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pl-20">
            <img src={img2.src} alt="" class="rounded-lg">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-52 font-bold my-10">
        <h1 class="text-blueMain text-3xl md:text-4xl text-center">
            The Triaso team understands that proper material handling and storage are key to optimal performance and durability
        </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full bg-grisSubP">
        <div class="w-full -skew-y-1 overflow-hidden bg-bgBeige">
            <div class="w-full px-8 lg:px-52 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 py-10 text-black skew-y-1">
                <div class="p-4 font-bold rounded-2xl">
                    <h1 class="text-lg md:text-xl">Durable Construction</h1><br>
                    <p class="text-grisT text-base md:text-lg font-thin">
                        Our bin units are engineered with wear-resistant materials
                        that perform exceptionally under abrasive and heavy loads. Their robust construction provides 
                        long-term reliability, the system remains reliable even under the harshest working conditions.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 font-bold rounded-2xl">
                    <h1 class="text-lg md:text-xl">Customizable Settings</h1><br>
                    <p class="text-grisT text-base md:text-lg font-thin">
                        The dosing system provides the flexibility to meet the specific demands of each project.
                         With options for both manual and automatic adjustment, it allows precise control of 
                         material flow.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="my-10 w-full flex justify-center">
            <img src={bin.src} alt="" class="max-h-[400px]">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 md:gap-10 items-start justify-center">
        <div class="col-span-2 flex justify-start md:justify-center">
            <Image src={binUnit1} alt="" class="w-3/4 md:w-full"/>
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-3 flex flex-col items-start h-full justify-center lg:pr-52 pr-8 md:pl-0 pl-8">
            <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-bold">Precision Dosing <br>Systems in <br>Bin Units</h1><br>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-thin text-grisT text-justify">Our bin units are equipped with advanced dosing systems designed for optimal
                 precision and reliability. These systems ensure accurate material flow and
                  distribution, meeting the demands of even the most stringent project
                   requirements.
            </p><br>
            <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-3 md:gap-6 pr-10">
                <AcordeonItem client:only title="High-Precision Sensors" content="Integrated sensors monitor material levels in real time, allowing for precise control of dosing quantities and preventing overflows or shortages.">
                </AcordeonItem>
                <AcordeonItem client:only title="Adjustable Flow Rates" content="The system allows operators to modify the flow rate, accommodating a wide range of materials, from fine aggregates to larger-sized rocks or sand.">
                </AcordeonItem>
                <AcordeonItem client:only title="Consistent Material Distribution" content="Ensures uniform dosing to maintain a balanced mixture in downstream operations, such as mixing or crushing processes.">
                </AcordeonItem>
                <AcordeonItem client:only title="Automated Controls" content="Equipped with programmable logic controllers (PLCs), the system can be automated for consistent and repeatable performance across different projects.">
                </AcordeonItem>
                <AcordeonItem client:only title="Anti-Clogging Mechanism" content="Specially designed chutes and gates minimize the risk of blockages, ensuring a smooth and uninterrupted material flow.">
                </AcordeonItem>
                <AcordeonItem client:only title="Energy-Efficient Operation" content="Engineered to optimize power usage, reducing operational costs while maintaining high performance.">
                </AcordeonItem>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</div>
<script is:inline>
    function toggleDropdown() {
        const dropdown = document.getElementById("extradiv2");
        const arrow = document.getElementById("dropdown-arrow2");
        
        if (dropdown.style.maxHeight === "0px" || !dropdown.style.maxHeight) {
            // Abrir dropdown
            dropdown.style.maxHeight = dropdown.scrollHeight + "px";
            arrow.style.transform = "rotate(180deg)";
        } else {
            // Cerrar dropdown
            dropdown.style.maxHeight = "0";
            arrow.style.transform = "rotate(0deg)";
        }
    }
</script>
